<br>
I've gotten the 2nd set, and next is to deliver Animist Poren's seal to Mahron Sood, an NPC who is either very well hidden in town, or not in the zone.<br>
<br>
Anyone get this far &amp; have any luck finding him?<br>
<br>
Thx in advance! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uvainmindbender.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Vain Mindbender</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/7/01 11:27:54 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> sood</span><hr size=1> Can be found outside the castle, in cat town, stuck in a corner, by an empty cage.  A tracker should be able to find him for you. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/upegglegthe3rd.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Peggleg the 3rd</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/hottopic.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/7/01 12:26:41 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: sood</span><hr size=1> Hmm, that rat eluded my tracker twice.  <br>
<br>
When you say outside the castle, do you still mean IN the kitty city zone, or is he in one of the adjacent newbie zones? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uazhdarkhos.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Azhdarkhos</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/7/01 3:44:19 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: sood</span><hr size=1> There are basically four sections to Shar Vahl city proper - the palace and it's courtyard (with a couple of buildings full of historians), the city center (with the arena, bank and some shops), and two lower rent districts to the north and south (with more vendors, residences, bars and barracks).<br>
<br>
Mahron Sood is in the city center section, back in a corner where the arena wall meets the city wall.  There are a couple of cages there, one with 'a caged rockhopper' (Mahron is trying to domesticate it.)<br>
<br>
Mahron will send you to talk with Kery Miann after you talk to him.  If you ask him where Kery Miann is, he will hint that she will be found near a loom.  Since it took me a lot longer to find Kery than Mahron, here's the lowdown - she's in a room on the second floor of one of the buildings in the city center section (not too far away from Mahron, actually).  I don't remember exactly which one, but there are a number of merchants downstairs, and its not the bank building, armory, arena, or alchemy shop (which narrows it down considerably.)<br>
<br>
Evidently, Vah Shir beastlords are expected to become master tailors someday... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/upegglegthe3rd.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Peggleg the 3rd</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/hottopic.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/7/01 4:36:34 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: sood</span><hr size=1> Thanks kindly for takin' the time to give such detail.  /bow <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><br><font color=#FF0000>- </font><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse>The Safehouse</a><font color=#FF0000> - </font><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13>Quests of Norrath</a> <font color=#FF0000> - </font><a href="http://www.thesafehouse.org">The Safehouse website</a><font color=#FF0000> - </font> <center><a href="http://www.guildboss.com"><img
